- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is relevant as the paper deals with the computation of solution sets of polynomial systems, which is a common problem in computational geometry. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is relevant as the paper discusses the computation of power series and the use of exact arithmetic libraries.
